<%# ──────────────────────────── HERO ──────────────────────────── %>
<div class="invest-hero">
  <div class="invest-hero-inner">
    <span class="section-label" style="color: var(--color-steel);">Real Estate Investment</span>
    <h1 class="heading-display" style="color: #fff; margin-top: 0.5rem;">Invest</h1>
    <p style="max-width: 34rem; margin: 1.25rem auto 0; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.75;">
      Access real estate investment opportunities backed by tangible
      property. Whether you are starting out or scaling up, we help
      you put capital to work in real assets.
    </p>
    <div class="ctx-dark" style="margin-top: 2rem; display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center;">
      <%= btn_tag "Start a Conversation", "https://calendly.com/anthony-socalkeys" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%# ──────────────────────────── VALUE PROP ──────────────────────────── %>
<div class="container-wide section">
  <div class="home-grid-2">
    <div>
      <span class="section-label">The Opportunity</span>
      <p class="heading-1">Real Property.<br>Real Returns.<br>Real Simple.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="text-body">
        Real estate has long been one of the most reliable ways to build
        wealth. But getting access to quality deals, structuring them
        properly, and managing them takes time, knowledge, and
        relationships most people do not have.
      </p>
      <p class="text-body" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
        That is where we come in. Linchpin Realty opens the door to
        investment opportunities across property types and capital levels,
        with the infrastructure and oversight to do it right.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%# ──────────────────────────── INVESTMENT PATHS ──────────────────────────── %>
<div style="background: var(--color-smoke); border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
  <div class="container-wide section">
    <span class="section-label">Ways to Invest</span>
    <p class="heading-1" style="margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">Investment Paths</p>

    <div class="home-grid-3 loans-types-grid">
      <div class="card-elevated" style="padding: 2rem;">
        <p class="heading-3">Private Lending</p>
        <div class="divider" style="margin: 1rem 0;"></div>
        <p class="text-body">
          Fund individual hard money loans secured by real property. You
          select the deals, set your criteria, and earn interest on
          deployed capital with first-position lien protection.
        </p>
        <ul class="loans-feature-list">
          <li>Asset-backed, first-position liens</li>
          <li>Defined terms and rates</li>
          <li>Choose your own deals</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card-elevated" style="padding: 2rem;">
        <p class="heading-3">Property Acquisition</p>
        <div class="divider" style="margin: 1rem 0;"></div>
        <p class="text-body">
          Invest directly in income-producing or value-add properties.
          We source, evaluate, and manage acquisitions so you can
          participate without handling the operational details.
        </p>
        <ul class="loans-feature-list">
          <li>Residential and commercial</li>
          <li>Value-add and stabilized</li>
          <li>Hands-on management by our team</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card-elevated" style="padding: 2rem;">
        <p class="heading-3">Joint Ventures</p>
        <div class="divider" style="margin: 1rem 0;"></div>
        <p class="text-body">
          Partner with us on specific projects. Joint ventures let you
          participate at a deeper level in deals where both parties
          bring something to the table: capital, expertise, or both.
        </p>
        <ul class="loans-feature-list">
          <li>Structured partnership terms</li>
          <li>Shared upside on projects</li>
          <li>Full transparency on deal structure</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%# ──────────────────────────── WHY INVEST WITH US ──────────────────────────── %>
<div class="container-wide section">
  <span class="section-label">Why Linchpin</span>

  <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 2rem;" class="lenders-benefits-grid">
    <div class="card" style="padding: 2rem;">
      <p class="heading-3">Deal Access</p>
      <p class="text-body" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
        We source opportunities through direct relationships, not
        listings. You see deals that are not available to the general
        market.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card" style="padding: 2rem;">
      <p class="heading-3">Underwriting Discipline</p>
      <p class="text-body" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
        Every deal is evaluated on its fundamentals: property value,
        borrower track record, exit strategy, and market conditions.
        We pass on more deals than we take.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card" style="padding: 2rem;">
      <p class="heading-3">Alignment of Interest</p>
      <p class="text-body" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
        We invest alongside our partners. When you win, we win.
        That alignment keeps us disciplined and accountable on
        every deal we bring to the table.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card" style="padding: 2rem;">
      <p class="heading-3">Clear Communication</p>
      <p class="text-body" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
        You will always know where your money is, how a project is
        progressing, and what comes next. No black boxes, no
        quarterly surprises.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%# ──────────────────────────── WHO THIS IS FOR ──────────────────────────── %>
<div style="background: #000;">
  <div class="container-wide ctx-black" style="padding-top: 4rem; padding-bottom: 4rem;">
    <div class="home-grid-2">
      <div>
        <span class="section-label" style="color: var(--color-steel);">Getting Started</span>
        <p class="heading-1" style="color: #fff;">No Minimum.<br>No Gatekeeping.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); line-height: 1.75; font-size: 0.9375rem;">
          We work with investors at every level. Whether you have $50K
          to deploy or $5M, the conversation starts the same way: what
          are your goals, what is your timeline, and what kind of
          involvement do you want?
        </p>
        <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); line-height: 1.75; font-size: 0.9375rem; margin-top: 1rem;">
          We will walk you through what is available, how each
          opportunity is structured, and help you decide what fits.
          No pressure, no pitch.
        </p>
        <div style="margin-top: 2rem;">
          <%= btn_tag "Schedule a Call", "https://calendly.com/anthony-socalkeys" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%# ──────────────────────────── CTA ──────────────────────────── %>
<div style="background: var(--color-navy);">
  <div class="container-wide ctx-navy" style="padding-top: 4rem; padding-bottom: 4rem; text-align: center;">
    <div style="max-width: 36rem; margin: 0 auto;">
      <p class="heading-1" style="color: white;">Ready to Build?</p>
      <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); margin-top: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; font-size: 0.9375rem;">
        Let us know what you are looking for. We will tell you
        what we have and whether it makes sense for you.
      </p>
      <div style="margin-top: 2rem; display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center;">
        <%= btn_tag "Schedule a Call", "https://calendly.com/anthony-socalkeys" %>
        <%= btn_tag "Email Us", "mailto:anthony@linchpinrealty.com" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%# ──────────────────────────── RELATED ARTICLES ──────────────────────────── %>
<% if @invest_blogs.any? %>
  <div class="container-wide section">
    <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
      <div>
        <span class="section-label" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">From the Knowledge Base</span>
        <p class="heading-1">Investment Insights</p>
      </div>
      <%= btn_tag "View All Articles", knowledge_index_path(category: "investing") %>
    </div>
    <div class="knowledge-grid">
      <% @invest_blogs.each do |blog| %>
        <%= render "shared/blogs/blog_card", blog: blog %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
<% end %>
